### Pollution Data Aggregator API Tests

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000


### Get Most Polluted Cities (Default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities

### Get Most Polluted Cities with pagination parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?page=1&limit=5

### Get Most Polluted Cities with country filter (France)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?country=FR&page=1&limit=10

### Get Most Polluted Cities with different country (US)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?country=US&page=1&limit=5

### Get second page with small limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?page=2&limit=3

### Test larger limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?limit=20

### Test edge cases - page 0 (should default to 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?page=0&limit=5

### Test edge cases - negative page (should default to 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?page=-1&limit=5

### Test edge cases - invalid limit (should default to 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cities?page=1&limit=0

